  "texts": [
    "Attempts to answer it (e.g.",
    "Hakli and Mäkelä 2019; Coeckelbergh 2020; Constantinescu et al. 2022) have failed to materialise a consensus on the necessary and sufficient preconditions for ascribing responsibility.",
    "An alternative route towards \"moral machines\", then, needs to answer why the new attempt will succeed-a philosophical question-and give an indication of the practical programme to be followed-a technical question.",
    "My chief contention is that Foucault's work can inform both answers.",
    "Nor should this be seen as merely a question of AI morality: it is potentially about mutual alignment in other dimensions of value: epistemic, cultural or aesthetic."
  ],
